snippet.title: THE BENGAL FILES Official Trailer | Vivek Agnihotri | Abhishek A | Pallavi J | Zee Studios | 5 Sept
snippet.description:
From the makers of The Kashmir Files and The Tashkent Files, here is the official trailer of THE BENGAL FILES, the powerful conclusion to the trilogy by two-time National Award-winning filmmaker Vivek Ranjan Agnihotri.

A presentation by: Tej Narayan & Snehlatha Agarwal and I Am Buddha

Directed by: Vivek Ranjan Agnihotri
Produced by: Abhishek Agarwal, Pallavi Joshi and Vivek Ranjan Agnihotri 
Worldwide Release: Zee Studios
Music: Zee Music Co.
Starring: Mithun Chakraborty, Anupam Kher, Pallavi Joshi, Darshan Kumaar, Simratt Kaur

This September, witness the untold truth of the Hindu genocide.

#TheBengalFiles #RightToLife

snippet.title: Rao Bahadur | Teaser | Satya Dev | Venkatesh Maha | GMB | SriChakraas | A+S | Summer 2026
snippet.description:
Rao Bahadur is a psychological drama set against the backdrop of a fading aristocracy - Made in Telugu, for the world.
 
Directed by acclaimed filmmaker Venkatesh Maha and starring the versatile Satya Dev as Rao Bahadur, the film is presented by Superstar Mahesh Babu & Namrata Shirodkar’s GMB Entertainment and produced by A+S Movies and SriChakraas Entertainments.
 
Releasing Summer 2026, in Theaters worldwide.
 
Genre - Psychological Drama, Suspense, Dark Comedy, Magical Realism.
 
 
Cast and Crew Details:
 
Cast - Satya Dev, Vikas Muppala, Deepa Thomas, Bala Parasar, Anand Bharathi, Pranay Vaka, Kunal Kaushik, Master Kiran and others.
 
Presented by - GMB Entertainment
Banners - SriChakraas Entertainments, A+S Movies, Mahayana Motion Pictures
Producers - Chinta Gopalakrishna Reddy, Anurag Reddy, Sharath Chandra
Writer, Director & Editor - Venkatesh Maha

snippet.title: SHANKARA (Official Video)I Power Star Pawan Singh I Kingstuff IGanesh Acharya I Ullumanati I Mahadev
snippet.description:
SHANKARA (Official Video) I Pawan Singh I Kingstuff I Ganesh Acharya I Ullumanati IMahadev Song 2025 #pawansingh #mahadev #pawansinghnewsong #shiv 

 
🔥 “Shankara” The New Age Mahadev Anthem is here! Experience the power, devotion, and energy like never before with Power Star Pawan Singh in this electrifying musical journey, directed and choreographed by Bollywood legend Ganesh Acharya.
 
OUT NOW – Witness the magic before the full release!

👉 Don’t forget to LIKE, COMMENT, SHARE & SUBSCRIBE for more Mahadev songs, Bhojpuri hits, and power-packed performances by Pawan Singh.
 
⸻
 
🎵 Song Credits
 
Audio

🎤 Singer : Power Star Pawan Singh
🎤 Rap: Kingstuff
🎼 Music & Lyrics: Ullumanati
🎼 Mix Master : Amit Monga

 
Video
Cast: Power Star Pawan Singh
Director & Choreographer: Ganesh Acharya
DOP: Ajay Pandey
Editor: Manoj Magar
Online Editor : Sayan Mal
Colorist : R P Singh
VFX : 4K Visuals 
Costumes : Jayshree 
Line Production : Monty Productions 
 
⸻
 
Produced by: Rashmi Devi Films Productions Pvt. Ltd.
Digital Partner: Global Music Junction Pvt. Ltd.
Promotions: RD Music & Records Team
Poster Design: Aman Kalsi
 
⸻

Lyrics : 

Bina tere ye kut halahal
Kaun hai peene wala re
Kal kut ka kare varan wo
Kaun hai jeene wala re
Bhal chandra bole bhandari 
Aan padi hai vipda bhari
Kasht niware kaun humaro
Surpati aye sharan tihari

Kal garal ye kanth ramaye vastu digambara shankara


Shankara Shankara
Vishambhara 
Shankara


bethe dhyaan magan bje dadum dum dum damru tera
bethe atal atari bhole ka kailash pe dera
vipda padi asur Gano pe sbne tera naam pukara
bachalo mahade sb dekhen ab rasta tera
pee gye bhole vish ka payala 
dhehke ab kanth mein jawala
gal neela padne lga toh
Gora maiyan ne smbhala
bethe fr dhyaan m bhole
har koi har har bole
gunje fr naam tera jai jai ho
vishambhraaaaaaa


Tere gale mai jo mala bhujango ki
Saje hai kanth mai visdhar bada
(Tere gale mai samaya jo pyala ye
Jawala ka na se bhayankar sada) x2

(Bane sanghni aadi teri 
Anhad naad samadi teri
Teen bhuwan mai kaun hai duja 
Kate hai jissay vyadi meri) x2

Bhujunga bhusan dhyan dharo re ab to maheswara


shankara Shankara
Visambhara
shankara

snippet.title: #Video | पित्तल के दाना | Pittal Ke Dana | Raushan Rohi New Song | Tanya Tiwari  | New Bhojpuri Song
snippet.description:
"पित्तल के दाना" एक नया और जोशीला भोजपुरी गीत है, जिसे रौशन रोही ने अपनी दमदार आवाज़ में गाया है और तान्या तिवारी ने शानदार अदाओं से सजाया है। इस गाने में देसी मिज़ाज, धमाकेदार बीट्स और मनोरंजन का भरपूर तड़का है, जो इसे सुनने और देखने वालों को झूमने पर मजबूर कर देता है।

Subscribe to our channel for more Bhojpuri Songs:
https://youtube.com/c/SaregamaHumBhojpuri

Credits:-

Song Name - Pittal Ke Dana
Hindi - पित्तल के दाना
Singer - Raushan Rohi
Featuring - Tanya Tiwari 
Music - Pappu Bhai
Lyrics - Raja Roshan 
Composer - Roshan Rohi
Mix & Master - Ankit Ahir
Director - Pawan Pathak 
Choreographer -Sahil Raj
Dop - Rahul Yadav
Editor - Rohan 
Di - Rohit Singh

Lyrics:-

F अरे हमर फेरा में केतना हो गेलै राजा से रंक,
अब तू ऐन बजावे रंगदारी वाला शंख।
अरे भले डरो हकौ तोरा से पूलिस थाना रे,
M जे रेट में किनोही तू सोना के खजाना गे,
उ रेट में किनोही हम पित्तल के दाना गे।

अंतरा 1
F अरे तोरा जैसन ढेरे हम देखलिऐ गुंडा रंगदार,
हमरा न बतावे रे छौड़ा कि केतना में आवै हथियार।
अरे जूटो होतौ ढंग से न घर के खर्ची खाना रे,
M जे रेट में किनोही तू सोना के खजाना गे,
उ रेट में किनोही हम पित्तल के दाना गे।

अंतरा 2
F अरे जवन कमवा करो ही उहे करो है हमर खनदान,
जेतना नय तोरा होतौ रे छौड़ा ओतना है हमर पहचान।
अरे राजा रौशन रोहिया तू त लागो ही निकामा रे,
M जे रेट में किनोही तू सोना के खजाना गे,
उ रेट में किनोही हम पित्तल के दाना गे।

#raushanrohi 
#saregamahumbhojpuri 
#bhojpuri

#bhojpurimusic 
#bhojpurivideo

A new Malayalam movie starring Madhav Suresh, Saiju Kurup, Shine Tom Chacko, Maqbool Salmaan, Nandu, M.A. Nishad, Sibi Thomas, Alencier, Noby, Kutty Akhil, Amith, Anna Rajan, Sminu Sijo and Ambika.

snippet.title: Thama Teaser Announcement | Ayushmann, Rashmika, Paresh, Nawazuddin| Dinesh | In Cinemas This Diwali
snippet.description:
Independence Day Special!
The No. 1 Hindi film Stree 2 turns 1 today 🎉

To celebrate, Dinesh Vijan expands the Maddock Horror-Comedy Universe with THAMA.

The World of Thama unveils Tuesday, Aug 19 — your first glimpse at the sarvashaktishaali villain set to redefine fear.
The film storms into cinemas this Diwali 2025.

Brace yourself — this chapter is a love story, wilder and deadlier than anything you’ve seen before.

#WorldOfThama #MaddockFilms #Diwali2025

Featuring: ‪Ayushmann Khurrana‬, Rashmika Mandanna, Paresh Rawal & Nawazuddin Siddiqui
Directed by: Aditya Sarpotdar
Produced by: Dinesh Vijan & Amar Kaushik
Written By: Niren Bhatt, Suresh Mathew & Arun Falara 
Co-Producers: Sharada Karki Jalota & Pooja Prem Patheja 
Music Composer: Sachin–Jigar
Lyrics: Amitabh Bhattacharya

Welcome to my channel!
I create Mashup, Fan-Made, and Concept Trailers by combining and editing footage from one or multiple movies. These trailers offer a fresh take on existing films, reimagine stories, or even create entirely new movie concepts.
Mashup trailers are a creative way to change the genre, storyline, or focus of a film. For example, a comedy can be transformed into a thriller, or different movies can be combined to create a crossover that doesn’t exist. These edits allow fans to see their favorite actors and films in a whole new light.
By mixing and re-editing scenes, I aim to build excitement for upcoming releases, highlight unique ideas, and bring cinematic "what-if" scenarios to life. Since these are creative remixes, they may be protected under fair use.

Software Used:
🎬 Adobe Premiere Pro 
🎨 Adobe After Effects 
🖼️ Adobe Photoshop

Through this roast, I expose their lack of observation towards Kerala’s culture, highlight the forced performances, and sarcastically break down why this trailer fails to connect with Malayali viewers.

सुन्दरकाण्ड में हनुमान जी का सीता माता को खोजने के लिए की गयी लंका यात्रा का सम्पूर्ण मनमोहक बखान किया गया है।

snippet.title: Franklin & Shinchan vs The Dog Mafia! 🐶🚔 | GTA 5 Malayalam Police Story Part 2
snippet.description:
Franklin and Shinchan are back in Part 2 of our GTA 5 Malayalam Police Story! 🔥
After Chop gets kidnapped, Franklin takes a goon hostage to find the truth. But things get out of hand when a new villain Butcher is revealed — a dangerous man who runs a dog smuggling company called Butcher & Co. 🐕✈️

Shinchan accidentally discovers Chop trapped among many other dogs in cages. With time running out, Franklin and Shinchan rush to the airport to stop Butcher from smuggling the dogs to China. Will they save Chop in time? Watch till the end for the epic airport combat and rescue mission! 💥🐾

👉 Don’t forget to Like 👍, Share ❤️, and Subscribe 🔔 to The Mallu Don for more funny GTA 5 Malayalam story videos featuring Franklin, Shinchan, Shiranui, and more!

After Chop gets kidnapped, Franklin takes a goon hostage to find the truth. But things get out of hand when a new villain Butcher is revealed — a dangerous man who runs a dog smuggling company called Butcher & Co. 🐕✈️

Shinchan accidentally discovers Chop trapped among many other dogs in cages. With time running out, Franklin and Shinchan rush to the airport to stop Butcher from smuggling the dogs to China. Will they save Chop in time? Watch till the end for the epic airport combat and rescue mission! 💥🐾

snippet.title: Minecraft Speedrunning (I'M LIVE AGAIN)
snippet.description:
Minecraft Speedrunning (I'M LIVE AGAIN)

DISCLAIMER: I am CHEATING! (Technically)

I am using mods that are not allowed in official leaderboard speedruns. This is practice for my videos, not for world records! I am also simulating ender eye calculation using a mod, I am only throwing the eyes to simulate a time spend, as official speedrunners use a bot to calculate the stronghold location off of 1/2 ender eyes.

I am also using no fog, optifine zoom, increased pearl rates (matching 1.16 rates), and a custom f3 menu with Nether Coordinates. (And maybe more, idk, who cares)

snippet.title: अच्युतम केशवम - Lyrical | Achyutam Keshavam Krishna Damodaram | Krishna Bhajan | Janmashtami 2025
snippet.description:
✨ अच्युतम केशवम् – श्रीकृष्ण भक्ति गीत ✨
 "अच्युतम केशवम्" एक अनुपम और मन को शांति देने वाला भजन है, जो भगवान श्रीकृष्ण और भगवान विष्णु की महिमा का गुणगान करता है। इसमें प्रभु के अनेक नाम प्रेमपूर्वक उच्चारित किए जाते हैं, जिनमें गहन आध्यात्मिक अर्थ निहित है।
यह भजन गाने से हृदय पवित्र होता है, दुख दूर होते हैं और परमात्मा की कृपा प्राप्त होती है। यह हमें पूर्ण समर्पण का मार्ग सिखाता है और याद दिलाता है कि भगवान सदैव हमारे रक्षक हैं।

✨ Achyutam Keshavam – A Devotional Krishna Bhajan ✨
 "Achyutam Keshavam" is a timeless and soul-soothing bhajan dedicated to Lord Krishna, praising their divine names, virtues, and forms. The bhajan beautifully recites various names of the Lord - Achyuta, Keshava, Narayana, and more - each carrying deep spiritual meaning.
Singing this bhajan is believed to purify the heart, remove sorrows, and bring the blessings of the Supreme Lord. It reminds devotees to surrender completely to God, trusting His eternal protection and grace.


🌸 Chant “Achyutam Keshavam” with devotion and invite divine bliss into your life.

Credits:
Singer - Saee Tembhekar
Music - Kamlesh Bhadkamkar
Lyrics - Traditional
Chorus - Shripad Lele, Vivek Naik, Unmesh Chandavarkar, Shardul Kavthekar, Seema Lele, Mrunmayi Dadke, Sapna Heman, Dhanashree Kashid
Flute - Varad Kathapurkar
Rhythm - Archis Lele, Hanumant Rawade, Vijay Jadhav, Anil Karanjavkar, Shashank Hadkar, Bharat Bhadkamkar
Guitar - Rahul Deo
Sound Engineer - Shrikrishna Sawant

To receive regular updates on devotional songs subscribe to us on the following link: https://www.youtube.com/BhaktiPrem

Lyrics:

अच्युतम केशवं कृष्ण दामोदरं,
राम नारायणं जानकी वल्लभम ।

कौन कहते हे भगवान आते नहीं,
तुम मीरा के जैसे बुलाते नहीं ।

कौन कहते है भगवान खाते नहीं,
बेर शबरी के जैसे खिलाते नहीं ।

कौन कहते है भगवान सोते नहीं,
माँ यशोदा के जैसे सुलाते नहीं ।

कौन कहते है भगवान नाचते नहीं,
गोपियों की तरह तुम नचाते नहीं ।

नाम जपते चलो काम करते चलो,
हर समय कृष्ण का ध्यान करते चलो ।

याद आएगी उनको कभी ना कभी,
कृष्ण दर्शन तो देंगे कभी ना कभी ।

Achyutam Keshavam Krishna Damodaram
 Ram Narayanam Janaki Vallabham

Kaun Kehte Hain Bhagwan Aate Nahin
 Tum Meera Ke Jaise Bulaate Nahin

Kaun Kehte Hain Bhagwan Khaate Nahin
 Ber Shabari Ke Jaise Khilaate Nahin
 
Kaun Kehte Hain Bhagwan Sote Nahin
 Maa Yashoda Ke Jaise Sulaate Nahin

Kaun Kehte Hain Bhagwan Naachte Nahin
 Gopiyon Ki Tarah Tum Nachaate Nahin

Naam Japte Chalo Kaam Karte Chalo
 Har Samay Krishna Ka Dhyaan Karte Chalo

Yaad Aayegi Unko Kabhi Na Kabhi
 Krishna Darshan To Denge Kabhi Na Kabhi

अच्युतम केशवम - Lyrical | Achyutam Keshavam Krishna Damodaram | Krishna Bhajan

यह भजन गाने से हृदय पवित्र होता है, दुख दूर होते हैं और परमात्मा की कृपा प्राप्त होती है। यह हमें पूर्ण समर्पण का मार्ग सिखाता है और याद दिलाता है कि भगवान सदैव हमारे रक्षक हैं।

✨ Achyutam Keshavam – A Devotional Krishna Bhajan ✨
 "Achyutam Keshavam" is a timeless and soul-soothing bhajan dedicated to Lord Krishna, praising their divine names, virtues, and forms. The bhajan beautifully recites various names of the Lord - Achyuta, Keshava, Narayana, and more - each carrying deep spiritual meaning.
Singing this bhajan is believed to purify the heart, remove sorrows, and bring the blessings of the Supreme Lord. It reminds devotees to surrender completely to God, trusting His eternal protection and grace.


🌸 Chant “Achyutam Keshavam” with devotion and invite divine bliss into your life.

Credits:
Singer - Saee Tembhekar
Music - Kamlesh Bhadkamkar
Lyrics - Traditional
Chorus - Shripad Lele, Vivek Naik, Unmesh Chandavarkar, Shardul Kavthekar, Seema Lele, Mrunmayi Dadke, Sapna Heman, Dhanashree Kashid
Flute - Varad Kathapurkar
Rhythm - Archis Lele, Hanumant Rawade, Vijay Jadhav, Anil Karanjavkar, Shashank Hadkar, Bharat Bhadkamkar
Guitar - Rahul Deo
Sound Engineer - Shrikrishna Sawant

To receive regular updates on devotional songs subscribe to us on the following link: https://www.youtube.com/BhaktiPrem

Lyrics:

अच्युतम केशवं कृष्ण दामोदरं,
राम नारायणं जानकी वल्लभम ।

कौन कहते हे भगवान आते नहीं,
तुम मीरा के जैसे बुलाते नहीं ।

कौन कहते है भगवान खाते नहीं,
बेर शबरी के जैसे खिलाते नहीं ।

कौन कहते है भगवान सोते नहीं,
माँ यशोदा के जैसे सुलाते नहीं ।

कौन कहते है भगवान नाचते नहीं,
गोपियों की तरह तुम नचाते नहीं ।

नाम जपते चलो काम करते चलो,
हर समय कृष्ण का ध्यान करते चलो ।

याद आएगी उनको कभी ना कभी,
कृष्ण दर्शन तो देंगे कभी ना कभी ।

Achyutam Keshavam Krishna Damodaram
 Ram Narayanam Janaki Vallabham

Kaun Kehte Hain Bhagwan Aate Nahin
 Tum Meera Ke Jaise Bulaate Nahin

Kaun Kehte Hain Bhagwan Khaate Nahin
 Ber Shabari Ke Jaise Khilaate Nahin
 
Kaun Kehte Hain Bhagwan Sote Nahin
 Maa Yashoda Ke Jaise Sulaate Nahin

Kaun Kehte Hain Bhagwan Naachte Nahin
 Gopiyon Ki Tarah Tum Nachaate Nahin

Naam Japte Chalo Kaam Karte Chalo
 Har Samay Krishna Ka Dhyaan Karte Chalo

Yaad Aayegi Unko Kabhi Na Kabhi
 Krishna Darshan To Denge Kabhi Na Kabhi
